reviewText:
Troy is the best, he's highly anointed and the dvd quality shocked me, it was absolutely awesome!!!
I recommend this to all my family members, specially the older one!!!..

You gotta give it to Troy Ramey. He's been round for a long time. He and the Soul Searchers bring that good ole traditional quartet sound every time. You can put this on and have a nice cozy time. He Brought Me Out!
